{
  "id": "62a96d3c312d570021432a64",
  "title": "性食考",
  "created": 1655270718,
  "updated": 1655270837,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62a96d3c312d570021432a64",
      "text": "性食考",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270718,
      "updated": 1655270718
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3de60035000057f78d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/550b0575e147835c5695a6d50c9ba655]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270718,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f78e",
      "text": "[https://www.iwanami.co.jp/book/b297922.html]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f78f",
      "text": "[赤坂憲雄]著　[岩波書店]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f790",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f791",
      "text": "内容",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f792",
      "text": "> 「食べちゃいたいほど，可愛い．」このあられもない愛の言葉は，〈内なる野生〉の呼び声なのか．食べる/交わる/殺すことに埋もれた不可思議な繋がりとは何なのか．近代を超え，いのちの根源との遭遇をめざす，しなやかにして大胆な知の試み．[神話]や[物語]，[祭り]や[儀礼]等を読み解き，学問分野を越境してめぐる，魅惑的な思索の旅．",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f793",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f794",
      "text": "目次",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f795",
      "text": "> はじめに",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f796",
      "text": "> 序　章　内なる野生",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f797",
      "text": "　> 野生の呼び声が聞こえる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f798",
      "text": "　> 汚れた野生の王国のかたわらで",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f799",
      "text": "　> いのちの根源は、ひとつか複数か",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f79a",
      "text": "> 第二章　異類婚姻譚",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f79b",
      "text": "　> 縫いぐるみの神話学",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f79c",
      "text": "　> [異類婚姻譚]の裂け目に",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f79d",
      "text": "　> 残酷なるもの、結婚とわかれ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f79e",
      "text": "　> ふつうの動物との結婚",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f79f",
      "text": "　> 生き物はみな人間に姿を変える",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a0",
      "text": "> 第三章　食と性と暴力と",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a1",
      "text": "　> [肉食]の終焉、そして[黙示録]的な未来へ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a2",
      "text": "　> 殺生と肉食をめぐる問い",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a3",
      "text": "　> 子どもを食べたがる怪獣たち",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a4",
      "text": "　> グリムの森の魔女と動物たち",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a5",
      "text": "　> 哄笑と残酷のゼロ地点に",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a6",
      "text": "　> 子どもの本のおいしい食べ方",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a7",
      "text": "> 第四章　動物をめぐる問題系",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a8",
      "text": "　> 糞と尿のあいだから生まれる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7a9",
      "text": "　> 自己からの距離、分類とタブー",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7aa",
      "text": "　> 内なる動物性からの逃走という逆説",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7ab",
      "text": "　> 穴とヴァギナの[精神分析]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7ac",
      "text": "　> 自己消費のタブーから共同の家へ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7ad",
      "text": "> 第五章　はじまりの神話",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7ae",
      "text": "　> 自己愛と残酷を超えるために",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7af",
      "text": "　> 性のはじまり、複製から自己創出へ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b0",
      "text": "　> 神話は泥の海を欲望する",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b1",
      "text": "　> [オノゴロ島]にて、聖なる結婚と死",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b2",
      "text": "> 第六章　女神の死",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b3",
      "text": "　> [九相図]のもとでの性と死の交歓",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b4",
      "text": "　> 腐敗と恐怖をめぐる形而上的な問い",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b5",
      "text": "　> [オホゲツヒメ]の死と作物の起源",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b6",
      "text": "　> [ハイヌウェレ]神話の原像",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b7",
      "text": "　> 女神の殺害と生殖のはじまり",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b8",
      "text": "　> 神話は祭りのなかで再演される",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7b9",
      "text": "> 第七章　大いなる口",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7ba",
      "text": "　> [ケガチ]の庭に饗宴が幕を開ける",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7bb",
      "text": "　> 戦場で語られた鳥喰い婆の昔話",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7bc",
      "text": "　> 大いなる口は小さな劇場である",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7bd",
      "text": "　> [食わず女房]、または拒食の根っこに",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7be",
      "text": "　> ふたつの口が妖しい出会いを果たすとき",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7bf",
      "text": "> 第八章　生け贄譚",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c0",
      "text": "　> 桜の樹の下は魂鎮めの現場である",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c1",
      "text": "　> まな板と箸と庖丁、痛みの記憶とともに",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c2",
      "text": "　> 贖罪の供犠と儀礼化、その終焉へ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c3",
      "text": "　> 桟敷には根源的な暴力が埋もれている",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c4",
      "text": "> 終　章　愛の倒錯",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c5",
      "text": "> あとがき",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c6",
      "text": "> 主な参考文献",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c8",
      "text": "試し読み：[https://www.iwanami.co.jp/moreinfo/tachiyomi/0061207.pdf]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7ca",
      "text": "[https://mainichi.jp/articles/20171010/org/00m/040/008000c SUNDAY LIBRARY：著者インタビュー　赤坂憲雄　『性食考』 | 毎日新聞]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7cb",
      "text": "[https://www.sankei.com/article/20171022-NHSKA3KKOJLRFAIR5SFTXAMSWQ/ 【書評】「食と性」生々しくも悪趣味でなく　『性食考』赤坂憲雄著（1/2ページ） - 産経ニュース]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7cc",
      "text": "[https://tadeku.net/83004/ こんなにおいしい本は、今までに食べたことがない！『性食考』をいただきます。 | 蓼食う本の虫]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7cd",
      "text": "[https://note.com/chishu_ryu/n/n4232e9b60c0a 性食考(感想)_食べることが、性や暴力に結びつくこと｜chishu_ryu｜note]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7d0",
      "text": "面白すぎて一気読みしました[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7d1",
      "text": "　性と食と[タブー]についての著者によるユニークな思索をまとめた、あまり類のない本です（エッセイ風）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7d2",
      "text": "　前々から漠然と「性(欲)」と「食(欲)」にはつながりがあるよな～と感じていましたが、この点について数多くの興味深い引用やアイデアを伴いつつ言語化されている刺激的な読み物です",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
    {
      "id": "62a96d3ee60035000057f7d3",
      "text": "　いちおう注意しておくと、本書では脳科学的な背景は追及されていません",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1655270719,
      "updated": 1655270719
    },
